window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Damien:</b></p> <p>I never thought I could fall in love. I never wanted to, until her.</p> <p>She makes my body and mind crazy. I need to protect her. I need to make her mine. I would die for her. I would kill for her, and I do.</p> <p><b>Bella:</b></p> <p>I left the English countryside and relocated to London to follow my dreams—or was it to escape my past?</p> <p>My career and a fresh start is all that is on my mind—until him.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
